entries.npc_1_1: You there! You have the look of someone who spends their time with unsavory characters. Would you be interested in knowing where others of your kind can be found? I'm sure these hired killers have a lot of credits just laying around. Interested?
entries.npc_2_1: Yes, yes you looked like someone who would be motivated by greed. I'll mark it on your datapad. Make sure you tell everyone you know.  That'll teach these Maulers to turn me down. Ha! Their secret base isn't so secret anymore, is it?
entries.npc_3_1: Oh! MY attitude? You don't like MY attitude? I'll have you know I'm one of the most well respected people within the higher circles of the Naboo Nobility. You, on the other hand, look to be nothing more than a simple street narglatch! Be off with you.
entries.npc_4_1: There's a group of assas...er, I mean to say, exterminators who are well known for their skills. Well, they turned down my money, and I'll have none of that! I'm making it a point that everyone knows where their base is to teach them a lesson! Interested?
entries.npc_backtowork_1: Yes, yes you looked like someone who would be motivated by greed. I'll mark it on your datapad. Make sure you tell everyone you know! That'll teach these Maulers to turn me down. Ha! Their secret base isn't so secret anymore, is it?
entries.npc_reset: Oh! MY attitude? You don't like MY attitude? I'll have you know I'm one of the most well respected people within the higher circles of the Naboo Nobility. You, on the other hand, look to be nothing more than a simple street narglatch! Be off with you.
entries.player_2_1: No thanks. I don't like your attitude.
entries.player_3_1: Why are you telling me this?
entries.player_reset: I decided to quit looking because I don't like your attitude.
entries.waypoint_description_1: A camp of assassins devoted to the former teachings of someone called Darth Maul
